{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "67a2eed8c8b73881fdaea35f", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 2, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": 90, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "MOG", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76b2c52ffa3c944600df"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6eb9a"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "67a2eb5da6d4514bf2d97611", "title": "JEE Main 2025 (29 Jan Shift 2)", "isVisible": true}], "question": {"text": "An electric dipole is placed at a distance of 2 cm from an infinite plane sheet having positive charge density $\\sigma_{\\mathrm{o}}$. Choose the correct option from the following.\n<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_main/Gn2asKgm1ffQ88sGYKMh4a6vTEncBGUgF4eqytt8P_0.original.fullsize.png\"/><br/>", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "rcyfi", "text": "Potential energy and torque both are maximum.", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "vYDNE", "text": "Torque on dipole is zero and net force is directed away from the sheet.", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "sYs9f", "text": "Torque on dipole is zero and net force acts towards the sheet.", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "1vchh", "text": "Potential energy of dipole is minimum and torque is zero.", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "Electric field due to sheet $E=\\frac{\\sigma}{2 \\varepsilon_0}$ \r\nand torque on dipole $\\vec{\\tau}=\\vec{P} \\times \\vec{E}$ \r\nhere $\\vec{\\tau}=0$ \r\nand $U=-\\vec{P} \\cdot \\vec{E} \\rightarrow$ should be minimum", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "masterId": "MOGJMPYQ250129020045", "priority": "Priority A", "isRemoved": false, "updatedAt": "2025-03-13T11:54:54.639Z", "updated_by": "65d